framework_component_specs.TableOfContents:
# TableOfContents — React Router (`.tsx`)

## Purpose
Auto-collapsing table of contents for React Router article routes. Displays primary `h2` anchors only, removes emoji from labels, and groups `h3` items under their preceding `h2` internally. Uses indigo link styling and native hash anchors for same-page navigation.

## Props

### Required
| Prop | Type | Description |
|------|------|-------------|
| `items` | `TocItem[]` | Array of TOC items with labels and anchors |

### Optional
| Prop | Type | Default | Description |
|------|------|---------|-------------|
| `title` | `string` | `'Contents'` | TOC section title |
| `ariaLabel` | `string` | `'Table of contents'` | Accessible label |
