# ArticleCardBySlug

## Purpose
React Router `.tsx` wrapper component that resolves article data from the articles registry by `slug` and renders an `ArticleCard`. Handles date formatting, author resolution, and fallback image selection automatically.

## Props

### Required
| Prop | Type | Description |
|------|------|-------------|
| `slug` | `string` | Article slug to look up in registry |

### Optional
| Prop | Type | Default | Description |
|------|------|---------|-------------|
| `ctaText` | `string` | `'Read more'` | Call-to-action button text |
| `className` | `string` | - | Additional CSS classes |
| `descriptionOverride` | `string` | - | Override the article description |
| `variant` | `'default' \| 'compact'` | `'default'` | Card size variant |
| `authorOverride` | `Author` | - | Override the article author |

